{"tid":667301,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好憎自己，覺得自己係零？","createTime":"2018-05-16T15:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T21:30:24.000Z","uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1f938e6cd2a0de8a2320e81b13c3e1ed7864f5cf","tid":667301,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T15:26:49.000Z","msg":"屋企係中學嗰陣離婚，阿媽搬走左<br />\n呢個係我人生第一個低潮期 但我唔識處理<br />\n返學俾人蝦到轉校，返工俾人恰到遞信，揾工揾到好頹，<br />\n<br />\n加上半工讀但d野又唔識，d同學討論功課我又唔識應人，好驚俾人以為我唔做野，依家只係人哋叫我做乜就做乜<br />\n<br />\n本身又無朋友，就算身邊另一半再撐你，都食唔晒d負能量，唔想辛苦人又辛苦自己，自己放棄自己都唔想連累人，所以我唔想浪費人地時間，對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可憐人必有可恨之處，因為我真係好廢好失敗，是零。"},{"pid":"19b30bb8a45ad6a6d0d5fb18f502244b1a087804","tid":667301,"uid":76098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T15:29:41.000Z","msg":"衰過你"},{"pid":"0f95c6a752444a69b2dce8d76032e3e9232bb62b","tid":667301,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19b30bb8a45ad6a6d0d5fb18f502244b1a087804","tid":667301,"uid":76098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T15:29:41.000Z","msg":"衰過你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T15:31:42.000Z","msg":"我都知世上好多人慘過我<br />\n但我真係覺得自己好廢 好憎自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3ba9c7bb5cb099ea73f2bb10fbad9d949efd46","tid":667301,"uid":5843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T15:33:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1cc438259c042a9db4669ca55b86602a54b6be5","tid":667301,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f95c6a752444a69b2dce8d76032e3e9232bb62b","tid":667301,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19b30bb8a45ad6a6d0d5fb18f502244b1a087804","tid":667301,"uid":76098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T15:29:41.000Z","msg":"衰過你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T15:31:42.000Z","msg":"我都知世上好